<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>中華民國運動促進協會 - Ｃ級運動按摩測驗系統</title>
    <style>
        /* 馬卡龍配色定義 */
        :root {
            --bg-color: #FDF6F5; /* 柔和淺粉底 */
            --primary: #FFB7B2; /* 蜜桃粉 */
            --primary-hover: #FFDAC1; /* 淺蜜桃 */
            --secondary: #E2F0CB; /* 柔和青草綠 */
            --accent: #B5EAD7; /* 薄荷綠 */
            --text-main: #5C4A4D; /* 護眼深咖啡色 */
            --text-light: #8B7E7F;
            --correct: #A0E8AF; /* 成功粉綠 */
            --incorrect: #FF9AA2; /* 警告粉紅 */
            --white: #FFFFFF;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, '微軟正黑體', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 1.25rem; /* 整體大字體設計 */
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* 首頁樣式 */
        #home-screen {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .main-title {
            font-size: 3.2rem;
            color: #E27D60;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .sub-title {
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            color: #85CDCA;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-large {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border: none;
            padding: 22px 50px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-large:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }

        /* 測驗區樣式 */
        #quiz-screen {
            display: none;
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 45px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        }

        .header-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 3px dashed var(--accent);
        }

        .timer {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #E8A87C;
            background: #FFF2E6;
            padding: 6px 18px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .progress {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .question-text {
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            color: #35988A;
        }

        .options-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .option-btn {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border: 3px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 22px;
            font-size: 1.55rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: left;
            color: var(--text-main);
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .option-btn:hover {
            background-color: #F0FBF7;
            border-color: #85CDCA;
        }

        .option-btn.selected {
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: #1A302B;
            border-color: #62C2A3;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .nav-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 45px;
        }

        .btn-nav {
            background-color: #C38D9E;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 35px;
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .btn-nav:hover { background-color: #A27684; }
        .btn-nav:disabled { background-color: #E0E0E0; cursor: not-allowed; color: #A0A0A0; }
        
        .btn-submit { background-color: #E27D60; }
        .btn-submit:hover { background-color: #C86D53; }

        /* 結果頁樣式 */
        #result-screen {
            display: none;
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 45px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        }

        .score-display {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .pass-status {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .status-pass { color: #1E6B3F; background-color: var(--correct); }
        .status-fail { color: #8B1A1A; background-color: var(--incorrect); }

        .review-box {
            background: var(--bg-color);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 8px solid var(--accent);
        }

        .review-box.wrong {
            border-left-color: var(--incorrect);
        }

        .review-question {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .review-answer {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .review-explanation {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #554477;
            background: #EAE4F2;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #926AA6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div id="home-screen">
        <div class="main-title">中華民國運動促進協會</div>
        <div class="sub-title">Ｃ級運動按摩</div>
        <button class="btn-large" onclick="startQuiz()">開始測驗 (隨機10題)</button>
    </div>

    <div id="quiz-screen">
        <div class="header-bar">
            <div class="progress">進度：<span id="current-q-num">1</span> / 10 題</div>
            <div class="timer">計時：<span id="time-display">00:00</span></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="question-text" id="question-text">題目載入中...</div>
        
        <div class="options-container" id="options-container">
            </div>

        <div class="nav-buttons">
            <button class="btn-nav" id="btn-prev" onclick="prevQuestion()">上一頁</button>
            <button class="btn-nav" id="btn-next" onclick="nextQuestion()">下一頁</button>
            <button class="btn-nav btn-submit" id="btn-submit" style="display:none;" onclick="submitQuiz()">繳交試卷</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="result-screen">
        <div class="score-display" id="score-display">0 分</div>
        <div class="pass-status" id="pass-status">狀態</div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 35px;">
            <button class="btn-nav" style="background-color: #41B3A3;" onclick="location.reload()">再測驗一次</button>
        </div>

        <h2 style="color: #35988A; font-size: 2.2rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #35988A; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 25px;">測驗題詳解</h2>
        <div id="review-container">
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

